\\t<li>Salary Advances<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Overtime Pay<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Ongoing Training<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Employee Engagement Activities etc.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nJob Type: Full-time\\r\\n\\r\\nSalary: \\u20b913,000.00 to \\u20b918,000.00 \\/year\\r\\n\\r\\nExperience:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Customer Handling: 1 year (Required)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Customer Service: 1 year (Required)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nEducation:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Secondary(10th Pass) (Required)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"post_title\":\"Customer Care Coordinator\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"customer-care-coordinator\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2019-01-16 09:43:25\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2019-01-16 09:43:25\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/job\\/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=99\",\"menu_order\":-1,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":102,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2019-01-15 19:46:05\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2019-01-15 19:46:05\",\"post_content\":\"Technologist to respond to the incidents \\/ issues reported by Customer predominantly through Voice Interaction and also through email, chat &amp; remote support.\\r\\n\\r\\nTechnologist to identify, investigate and diagnose the issue and take necessary action viz resolves or assigns the issue to right assignment group.\\r\\n\\r\\nFollows the incident life cycle as defined by process viz \\u2013 logging the incident with proper priority, categorization and documentation, performs follow up on all necessary incidents as defied in process with customer to ensure timely closure.\\r\\n\\r\\nGood to Have:\\r\\n\\r\\nTechnical Certifications like A+, Network +, Security +, CCNA, MCP, MCSP etc\\r\\n\\r\\nExperience should be from voice based technical support desk, supporting Americas\\/Europe\\/ EMEA etc Continent customers.\\r\\n\\r\\nDomestic tech support can be considered post evaluating on Voice and accent of candidate.\\r\\n\\r\\nBPO\\/ Call Center experience can be considered post evaluating the technical knowledge of the candidate.\\r\\n\\r\\nBachelor degree or 3 year diploma\",\"post_title\":\"Customer support Voice\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"customer-support-voice\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2019-01-15 19:52:24\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2019-01-15 19:52:24\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/job\\/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=102\",\"menu_order\":-1,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":108,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2019-01-15 20:02:40\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2019-01-15 20:02:40\",\"post_content\":\"Walk-in @ Capgemini for Customer Support - International Voice Process - Bangalore\\r\\n\\r\\nSkill: International Voice Process\\/ Semi Voice\\r\\n\\r\\nRole: Process Associate\\r\\n\\r\\nWork Location: Bangalore\\r\\n\\r\\nBusiness Unit: BPO\\r\\n\\r\\nExperience Required: 1- 3 Years\\r\\n\\r\\nEducation Criteria: Any Graduate\\r\\n\\r\\nInterview Date&amp; Time: ON 18th January between 5.00 P.M to 06.00 P.M\\r\\n\\r\\nVenue:\\r\\n\\r\\nCapgemini\\r\\n\\r\\n158 - 162 &amp; 165 - 170,\\r\\n\\r\\nEPIP Phase-2,\\r\\n\\r\\nWhitefield,\\r\\n\\r\\nBangalore 560066\\r\\n\\r\\nContact Person- Viji\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\nQualifications\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\nJob Responsibilities\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Should have minimum 1- 3 years of experience in International Voice process.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Excellent communication and conversation skills (Verbal and Written).<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Should have a great customer handling skills.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Knowledge of basic computer operations.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Courteous with strong customer service orientation.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Should have great interpersonal skills and ability to perform under pressure<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Clarify customer requirements; probe for and confirm understanding of requirements or problem.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nSpecifications:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Candidates willing to work in US Shifts only need to apply.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Candidates should have minimum of 50% in X, XII, Graduation with not more than 3yr gap in education and \\/career.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Please carry a copy of this mail along with your updated resume, passport size photo, photo ID proof and educational documents.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nPlease ignore the above mail if the above mentioned specifications do not match your profile\\/\\r\\n\\r\\nif you were part of CAPGEMINI interview in last 6 months.\",\"post_title\":\"Customer Support - Voice Process - Banking\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"customer-support-voice-process-banking\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2019-01-15 20:02:40\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2019-01-15 20:02:40\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/job\\/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=108\",\"menu_order\":-1,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":110,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2019-01-16 08:15:24\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2019-01-16 08:15:24\",\"post_content\":\"<div>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Respond to customer queries via inbound calls, emails, chat and web tickets within defined SLA\\u2019s<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Logging incidents and service requests, categorizing and prioritizing them, and managing their life cycle as per ITIL guidelines.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Update users about request status and close request when users are satisfied with solutions<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Level 1, Level 2 and Level 3 troubleshooting mainly related to desktop\\/OS, Custom and COTS applications, Exchange related, End devices, VPN, VOIP and share point as per guidelines in the knowledgebase.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Remote desktop troubleshooting. Escalate complex incidents \\/ requests to upstream technical groups<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Knowledge of Citirx is a must<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Preferrebly looking for immediate joiners<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Should be comfortable for:<\\/b>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>5 days working Night Shift May require to do Day shift during training and transition<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>2 Days Weekly Off. Any 2 Days of the week<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>9 Hours Login ( With 1 Hour Break )<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Excellent command on English (Verbal and Written)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<b>Other Benefits\\u00a0<\\/b>:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Pick up and Drop<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Global Standards work environment<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Proper Desk job<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Performance linked incentives<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"post_title\":\"Sr Tech. Support - SD\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"sr-tech-support-sd\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2019-01-16 08:15:24\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2019-01-16 08:15:24\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/job\\/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=110\",\"menu_order\":-1,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":115,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2019-01-16 10:10:50\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2019-01-16 10:10:50\",\"post_content\":\"<b>Position: HR \\u2013 Business Partner<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Position Background:<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>THIS IS FLIPKART: People are at the forefront of every revolution. From a two-man team to a workforce of over 30,000 - Flipkart is an organisation that is empowered by all kinds of people who meet on the mutual ground of e-commerce and work towards revolutionising the way India shops. Flipkart is one among India\\u2019s first companies to embrace a people-friendly work ethic. We realise that every Flipster - as we call ourselves - comes in to solve challenges; something that cannot be done in a place with an assembly line mentality. And so, over the years, we\\u2019ve worked to create a near-perfect workplace that ensures every Flipster is inspired and engaged constantly, be it a Monday or a Friday.<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>To carry forward the fast-paced growth, Flipkart is looking for an HR Business Partner. The HRBP would be a critical member of our team and would together help build a best place to work.<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Responsibilities:<\\/b>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Employee connect \\u2013 pulse on the ground and regular connects<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Organize and work independently on multiple tasks and complete assignments within specified deadlines.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Prepare and maintain accurate records, files and reports, including responsibility for maintaining personnel records.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Communicate effectively at all levels of staff and management<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Compile and analyze information, and do RCA for solutions to issues.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Advise on employment statutes, rules, regulations and policies affecting team members.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Recommend, develop, interpret and clarify personnel procedures and policies.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Assist in hiring and screening and interviewing candidates.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Maintain knowledge of and ensure compliance with employment-related laws and regulations<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Provide leadership in effective conflict resolution for all personnel<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Develop and implement human resources programs and policies<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Handling employee issues and assist in counseling employees and problem-solving<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Assist in hiring by providing job descriptions and by screening and interviewing candidates<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Develop, implement and participate in employee recognition programs<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Conduct E-sat surveys, exit interviews\\r\\n<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Must Have Skills:<\\/b>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Post-Graduation in HR preferably from Tier 1 institute<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>At least 3 years of professional experience across all HR disciplines, including employment, benefits, compensation, employee relations, training and development, workers compensation and conflict resolution.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Maintain confidentiality of sensitive information<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Experience working with a diverse workforce.<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Prior experience working with off-roll employees a plus<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Communicate effectively to a diverse audience<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Excellent time-management and problem-solving skills<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Work with close attention to detail\\r\\n<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<b>Desired Skills :\\r\\n<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Excellent interpersonal skills to facilitate interaction with the workforce<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Remain flexible in order to adapt to changes in work environment and take initiative<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"post_title\":\"Lead HR Partner\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"lead-hr-partner\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2019-01-16 10:35:11\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2019-01-16 10:35:11\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/job\\/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=115\",\"menu_order\":-1,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"}],\"found_posts\":\"6\",\"max_num_pages\":1}', 'no'),
