(29, 1, '2019-01-13 17:50:37', '2019-01-13 17:50:37', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Jobrr.com is the most innovative and largest online job portal in India. Founded in 2019, over the past decade, Jobrr.com has become a prominent name in the recruitment industry. The popularity of the portal is evident from the fact that it has crossed the 2.6 crore candidate landmark and has more than 3 lakh latest job vacancies from leading companies on the site. <br><br>Jobrr.com connects <g class=\"gr_ gr_16 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del\" id=\"16\" data-gr-id=\"16\">jobseekers</g> and recruiters by accurately matching candidate profiles to the relevant job openings through an advanced 2-way matching technology. While most job portals only focus on getting candidates the next job, <g class=\"gr_ gr_76 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"76\" data-gr-id=\"76\">Jobrr</g> focuses on the entire career growth of candidates. <br><br>As the industry shifts towards mobile, Jobrr.com is leading the transition and is the fastest growing job portal on mobile devices, witnessing a 100% YOY growth in mobile traffic and also offers on-the-go jobs through the <g class=\"gr_ gr_84 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"84\" data-gr-id=\"84\">Jobrr</g> Job Search App. <br><br><g class=\"gr_ gr_92 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"92\" data-gr-id=\"92\">Jobrr</g> works closely to bridge the gap between talent &amp; opportunities and offers end-to-end recruitment solutions. <g class=\"gr_ gr_100 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"100\" data-gr-id=\"100\">Jobrr</g> Job Fair brings candidates and top employers under one roof. While <g class=\"gr_ gr_108 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"108\" data-gr-id=\"108\">Jobrr</g> HR Conclave brings top HR leaders to share insights on <g class=\"gr_ gr_20 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"20\" data-gr-id=\"20\">latest</g> trends, innovations &amp; best practices in the HR industry. <g class=\"gr_ gr_117 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"117\" data-gr-id=\"117\">Jobrr</g> also has a large reach through its print product, <g class=\"gr_ gr_126 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"126\" data-gr-id=\"126\">Jobbr</g> Jobs – the Tuesday Job supplement of Hindustan Times– making it the only job portal with an integrated print and online offering</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2019-01-16 12:42:09', '2019-01-16 12:42:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/job/?page_id=29', 0, 'page', '', 0),
